<p align="center"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>新闻发布会现场（央广网记者 邓文辉 摄）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>此</span></span></span><span><span><span>次博览会以</span></span></span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span><span><span><span>‘</span></span></span><span><span><span>箱’约永州‘包’容天下”</span></span></span><span><span><span>为主题，</span></span></span><span><span><span>是今年</span></span></span><span><span><span>永州首次举办的大型展会，也是永州唯一纳入省级层面支持的展会</span></span></span><span><span><span>，</span></span></span><span><span><span>会期3天，专业观众</span></span></span><span><span><span>人数将达到8000人。</span></span></span><span><span><span>300余家国内皮具箱包玩具制鞋行业龙头企业、品牌企业、设备生产商和技术提供商</span></span></span><span><span><span>将参加展览，汇集</span></span></span><span><span><span>法国SMILEY、蒙娜丽莎、叶子王、标准、杰克、博克等</span></span></span><span><span><span>知名企业，旨在</span></span></span><span><span><span>通过会展的形式架起沟通的“桥梁”</span></span></span><span><span><span>，</span></span></span><span><span><span>促进</span></span></span><span><span><span>永州皮具箱包轻纺制鞋产业转型升级</span></span></span><span><span><span>和</span></span></span><span><span><span>皮具箱包玩具企业抱团发展，</span></span></span><span><span><span>打造国家重要先进制造业和内陆地区改革开放的高地，推动高质量发展。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>博览会期间，</span></span></span><span><span><span>将推出2020永州·蓝山国际皮具箱包博览会开幕式、皮具箱包玩具制鞋产业招商对接会暨签约仪式、皮具箱包玩具制鞋产业采购对接会、2020全国箱包新品原创设计时尚潮流发布会和皮具箱包玩具鞋业直播秀</span></span></span><span><span><span>等</span></span></span><span><span><span>五大主体活动</span></span></span><span><span><span>，</span></span></span><span><span><span>打造</span></span></span><span><span><span>开放、创新、合作、交流、共享的</span></span></span><span><span><span>皮具箱包行业盛会</span></span></span><span><span><span>。</span></span></span><span><span><span>博览会</span></span></span><span><span><span>展厅面积</span></span></span><span><span><span>达到</span></span></span><span><span><span>2万平方米，</span></span></span><span><span><span>将</span></span></span><span><span><span>设置魅力永州主题形象展区、皮具展区、箱包展区、玩具展区、鞋业展区、加工设备展区、原辅材料展区</span></span></span><span><span><span>和网上展区等8</span></span></span><span><span><span>大主体展区</span></span></span><span><span>。</span></span><span><span><span>魅力永州主题形象展区将</span></span></span><span><span><span>设置永州风景名胜一条街、永州特色小吃一条街、永州特色农产品一条街</span></span></span><span><span><span>等3条街</span></span></span><span><span><span>，</span></span></span><span><span><span>全方位展示</span></span></span><span><span><span>永州</span></span></span><span><span><span>独特的文化和美食元素</span></span></span><span><span><span>。</span></span></span><span><span><span>主办方还</span></span></span><span><span><span>将安排大巴车</span></span></span><span><span><span>到永州高铁站、郴州西高铁站、广州白云区三元里地铁口和狮岭富力环贸港专车接送</span></span></span><span><span><span>，</span></span></span><span><span><span>为采购商提供免费住宿</span></span></span><span><span><span>服务</span></span></span><span><span><span>，尊商重商</span></span></span><span><span><span>，</span></span></span><span><span><span>热情办会</span></span></span><span><span><span>。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
